---
// Transparency and trust section highlighting fair practices
---

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      
      <!-- Section Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <div class="transparency-badge mx-auto mb-4">
          üîç Complete Transparency
        </div>
        <h2 class="mb-6">
          How We're <span class="text-gradient">Different</span> From Other Agencies
        </h2>
        <p class="text-subtitle max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          While 99% of marketing agencies hide their costs and surprise clients with fees, 
          we believe in radical transparency. Here's exactly how we operate differently.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Comparison Grid -->
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-16">
        
        <!-- Other Agencies -->
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-8 text-slate-600">
            üì¢ What Other Agencies Do
          </h3>
          
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-6 bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-xl">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-red-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.293 4.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 8.586l4.293-4.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414L11.414 10l4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L10 11.414l-4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L8.586 10 4.293 5.707a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-red-800 mb-2">Hidden Pricing</h4>
                <p class="text-red-700 text-sm">"Starting from ¬£X" then surprise you with the real costs later</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-6 bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-xl">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-red-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.293 4.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 8.586l4.293-4.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414L11.414 10l4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L10 11.414l-4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L8.586 10 4.293 5.707a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-red-800 mb-2">Surprise Fees</h4>
                <p class="text-red-700 text-sm">Setup fees, admin fees, "emergency" charges that appear out of nowhere</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-6 bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-xl">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-red-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.293 4.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 8.586l4.293-4.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414L11.414 10l4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L10 11.414l-4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L8.586 10 4.293 5.707a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-red-800 mb-2">Upfront Payment</h4>
                <p class="text-red-700 text-sm">Demand 50-100% payment upfront before any work begins</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-6 bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-xl">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-red-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.293 4.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 8.586l4.293-4.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414L11.414 10l4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L10 11.414l-4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L8.586 10 4.293 5.707a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-red-800 mb-2">Vague Reporting</h4>
                <p class="text-red-700 text-sm">Complex reports with vanity metrics that don't show real business impact</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Fearnbell Marketing -->
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-8 text-slate-900">
            ‚ú® What Fearnbell Marketing Does
          </h3>
          
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-6 bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-200 rounded-xl">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-emerald-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-emerald-800 mb-2">Published Prices</h4>
                <p class="text-emerald-700 text-sm">Every service price is public on our website. No surprises, ever.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-6 bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-200 rounded-xl">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-emerald-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-emerald-800 mb-2">Zero Hidden Fees</h4>
                <p class="text-emerald-700 text-sm">The price we quote is exactly what you pay. No admin, setup, or surprise charges.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-6 bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-200 rounded-xl">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-emerald-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-emerald-800 mb-2">Fair Payment Plan</h4>
                <p class="text-emerald-700 text-sm">25% to start, then 25% each month for 3 months. Fair and manageable.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-6 bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-200 rounded-xl">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-emerald-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-emerald-800 mb-2">Clear ROI Reports</h4>
                <p class="text-emerald-700 text-sm">Simple reports showing actual business impact, revenue, and return on investment.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Trust Guarantees -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-white rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 border border-slate-200">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-8">Our Transparency Guarantees</h3>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Price Lock Promise</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Your quoted price will never change. Ever.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-emerald-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-emerald-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">No Hidden Fees</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Zero surprise charges. What you see is what you pay.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-amber-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-amber-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Fair Payment Terms</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">4 equal payments spread over 4 months.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Open Book Reports</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">See exactly where your money goes and results achieved.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Call to Action -->
      <div class="text-center mt-16">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Ready for Marketing That's Actually Fair?</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          No hidden costs. No surprise fees. No vague promises. Just transparent pricing, 
          clear communication, and results you can measure.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/calculator" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg hover-lift hover-glow">
            Calculate Your Exact Cost
          </a>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg hover-lift">
            Get Your Free Quote
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>